e":"Shanghai Knights","video":false,"overview":"When a Chinese rebel murders Chon's estranged father and escapes to England, Chon and Roy make their way to London with revenge on their minds.","genre_ids":[28,12,35,37],"popularity":2.1879,"vote_count":2393,"poster_path":"/vVNQStMlZS9mn2AKBEpadRunHgt.jpg","release_date":"2003-02-06","vote_average":6.14,"backdrop_path":"/AoXqOWzD0HGZttYi0wHMvvGJZhZ.jpg","original_title":"Shanghai Knights","original_language":"en"},{"id":274854,"adult":false,"title":"The Last Witch Hunter","video":false,"overview":"The modern world holds many secrets, but by far the most astounding is that witches still live among us; vicious supernatural creatures intent on unleashing the Black Death upon the world and putting an end to the human race once and for all. Armies of witch hunters have battled this unnatural enemy for centuries, including Kaulder, a valiant warrior who many years ago slayed the all-powerful Witch Queen, decimating her followers in the process. In the moments right before her death, the Queen cursed Kaulder with immortality, forever separating him from his beloved wife and daughter. Today, Kaulder is the last living hunter who has spent his immortal life tracking down rogue witches, all the while yearning for his long-lost family.","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"popularity":3.873,"vote_count":3791,"poster_path":"/dS9YdnJkxtKE2PKCSsxTaO7Jpf5.jpg","release_date":"2015-10-21","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/mXmvN6drkdU1PWFF92AGklEVIa3.jpg","original_title":"The Last Witch Hunter","original_language":"en"},{"id":20352,"adult":false,"title":"Despicable Me","video":false,"overview":"Gru is a supervillain determined to prove he’s the greatest by stealing the Moon. To pull off his plan, he adopts three orphaned girls—Margo, Edith, and Agnes—intending to use them as part of his scheme. However, as Gru bonds with the girls, his cold, villainous exterior begins to melt.","genre_ids":[10751,35,16,878,28],"popularity":11.872,"vote_count":15